As part of the VIth year clinical practice, 4 weeks can be used to prolong other placements or an elective placement can be performed either at a clinic, institute or other healthcare institution. The precondition for performing the elective placement is an agreement of the site to accept the student at agreed time period.
Scientific research can be accepted as elective placement with agreement of the supervisors of clinical practice.
At least 50 AMBOSS platform cases must be solved during the elective placement, the completion will be checked up on at the end of the semester.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the elective placement is implementing and using theoretical knowledge for practical clinical purposes at the department chosen by the student, at an institutions of health care administration or in scientific labs.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the course, the student will: -  have better practical understanding of the selected speciality
